Package system

Class User

java.lang.Object
system.User
Direct Known Subclasses:
Admin, Staff
public class User extends Object
class representing a generic user in the system. This class provides a common framework to handle different types of users.
Author:
FDAA 5

    • User

      public User(UserType userType, String accountId, String password, String name, Gender gender, int age, String branchName)
      Constructs a User with specified attributes.
      Parameters:
      userType - The type of user (e.g., ADMIN, STAFF, MANAGER).
      accountId - The unique identifier for the user.
      password - The user's password for system access.
      name - The user's full name.
      gender - The user's gender.
      age - The user's age.
      branchName - The name of the branch to which the user is assigned.
